  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Create your own cozy forest!</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Plant Seeds and Watch Them Grow</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/61b2cc990fa82133b33ad0eda1eba8f6.poster.avif?t=1764053902\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/61b2cc990fa82133b33ad0eda1eba8f6.webm?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/61b2cc990fa82133b33ad0eda1eba8f6.mp4?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the full lifecycle of trees: seed, sapling, adult tree, dead tree and fallen trunk. Each step creates a different habitat for other plants and animals.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fill Your Forest with Animals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/b46381898491e8f6dcd15f2678017409.poster.avif?t=1764053902\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/b46381898491e8f6dcd15f2678017409.webm?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/b46381898491e8f6dcd15f2678017409.mp4?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each animal has specific habitat needs you have to fullfill before adding them. Squirrels need trees, butterflies need flowers etc.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Click Animals to Make Them Poop and More</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/bde6394e1c3682b1480c2966fd46c160.poster.avif?t=1764053902\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/bde6394e1c3682b1480c2966fd46c160.webm?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/bde6394e1c3682b1480c2966fd46c160.mp4?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clicking on animals trigger different behaviors that influence the forest ecosystem: Moose poop, fertilizing the soil. Voles eat tree roots, damaging the tree. Foxes hunt other animals.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adapt to the Terrain or Terraform It to Your Needs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/2ba0564a05a44a36c7fd480205e7b47a.poster.avif?t=1764053902\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/2ba0564a05a44a36c7fd480205e7b47a.webm?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/2ba0564a05a44a36c7fd480205e7b47a.mp4?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create forests in diverse terrains including hills, lakes, mountains, fjords and wetlands. Terraform the terrain if you want even more control.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive Natural Disasters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/cead08a5dbc4f6d4f9b0ec43bd6f11df.poster.avif?t=1764053902\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/cead08a5dbc4f6d4f9b0ec43bd6f11df.webm?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/cead08a5dbc4f6d4f9b0ec43bd6f11df.mp4?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forest fires, storms and bark beetle swarms affect the forest in various ways. Can you use them to your advantage and create a thriving ecosystem?</p>",
