/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/cead08a5dbc4f6d4f9b0ec43bd6f11df.poster.avif?t=1764053902\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/cead08a5dbc4f6d4f9b0ec43bd6f11df.webm?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/cead08a5dbc4f6d4f9b0ec43bd6f11df.mp4?t=1764053902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forest fires, storms and bark beetle swarms affect the forest in various ways. Can you use them to your advantage and create a thriving ecosystem?</p>",
